== uNav ==

A map viewer & GPS Navigator for Ubuntu Touch.

== TIPS ==

=== Migrate favorites & history ===

Move & overwrite: ~/.local/share/navigator.costales/Databases/*.sqlite

The filename will change from one phone to another.
